urls.title: 1893 - JPunks: OG-Rex
urls.description: 65 million years ago, an asteroid rocketed towards Earth, an extinction-level event destined to wipe out an entire species… But it missed. Left to thrive, the dinosaurs evolved into the Jurassic Punks, a 3D misfit group of characters who are now the dominant species in the Metaverse, with the 7777 OG-REX leading the way. Jurassic Punks is a one-of-a-kind 3D generative NFT collection from professional VFX studio Meta-Labs. Built in Unreal Engine 5, utilizing state-of-the-art film quality Motion Capture to bring your metaverse ready NFTs to life, onto your screen and Digital Fashion show. NFTs Evolved!
